description.content:
Are you in need of professional and cost-effective WordPress development services? Look no further.


Teamseven (PVT) LTD is a registered software company with 7+ years of experience in software engineering and cloud solutions. We specialize in creating custom WordPress solutions, tailored to your specific needs. With our expertise, we can help you stand out with a winning web presence.


Our services include:

  • Custom Website Development
  • Theme Development and Customization
  • Plugin Development and Customization
  • WordPress Errors Fixing
  • Building Custom Templates
  • Social media & Payment gateway Integration (PayPal, Stripe, etc.)
  • Autoresponder Integration(MailChimp, Aweber, SendGrid)
  • E-commerce/WooCommerce
  • Fully Responsive Design
  • Mobile Friendly
  • SEO & Speed Optimization
  • No-Code Development (Elementor)


or any other task related to your WordPress Website.


WHY CHOOSE OUR SERVICES?

  • 7+ years Experience
  • 500+ Projects
  • 270+ Happy Clients
  • Fast Development
  • Low Cost
  • Friendly Relations 
  • Free Training
  • After Service Support
  • On Demand Video Consultation

questionsAndAnswers.question: Requirements to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
1). One or more reference websites that you like (this will give me an idea of your expectations). 
2). Logins to your cPanel. 
3). Logins to your WordPress (if already set up). If Not, I will install WordPress free of cost.
4). Theme files and URL if you already purchased.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Even if you don't know any programming language, You can easily edit your website. This is the power of WordPress and its page builders.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Hosting Services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, We provide hosting services starting at 7$/month. You can consult with us more about hosting via inbox.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Domain Services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we do not provide but I can assist you to buy a domain for your website through better registrars.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many revisions are offered?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we offer multiple revisions. Your 100% satisfaction is our first priority.
